      "text": "Today is Katie’s 22nd birthday.\n\nHer life was stolen at 20 years old.\n\nAs her dad, I should be celebrating with her—hearing her laugh, seeing who she was becoming, watching her build her life. Instead, I’m left with the memories of who she was and the reality of what was taken.\n\nKatie, you deserved more time. More life. More years.\n\nI miss you. I will keep saying your name. And as your father, I hold onto the day I get to be with you again and hear about all the adventures you’ve had since, with our Heavenly Father.\n\nHappy Heavenly 22nd Birthday.\n❤️❤️❤️❤️🙏🙏🙏🙏",
